modName: College of Winterhold to Star Wars Sith Academy
summary: A re-texture of the College of Winterhold to look similar to a Sith Academy
descriptionHtml:
I re-textured the College of Winterhold to look kinda like a Star Wars Sith Academy. It's a little flawed though :-( The entry gate won't display the Sith symbol properly. Sadly, I can't do anything about this without changing the mesh of the gate. If you want to use my stuff in your mod, all you have to do is ask. ;-) I hope you all like it!
8-)

-avenger86
